.main-contents-with-hint__inner
  = form_for @image, html: { class: "main-contents-with-hint__wrapper" } do |f|
    .main-contents-with-hint__main-wrapper
      .main-contents-with-hint__main
        .space-info-page__title-container
          .space-info-page__title 4 写真・動画
          .space-info-page__description
        %div
          //写真
          .create-space-sections__section
            .form-section-title__container
              .form-section-title__title-container
                = f.label :image, "必須", class: "form-section-title__required-label"
                .form-section-title__title 写真
              .form-section-title__description ゲストが実際に利用するスペース、設備等の画像を最低1枚追加してください。推奨サイズは1260x840です。ドラッグ＆ドロップで入れ替え可。クリックで拡大することができます。最大30枚まで追加できます。
            .photo-form__from-wrapper
              .photo-form__add
                %label.photo-form__add__mask
                  = fa_icon "plus", class: "icon"
                  %span 新規写真の追加
                  = f.file_field :uri
              .photo-list__container
                %ul
                  %li.photo-list__list-item
                    .photocard__container
                      .photocard__photo
                      .photocard__text
                        = f.text_area :about_image, placeholder: "閑静なオフィス街にあるビル内の施設です。", class: "photocard__text__textarea"
                  -# %li.photo-list__list-item
                  -#   .photocard__container
                  -#     .photocard__photo
                  -#     .photocard__text
                  -#       %textarea{placeholder: "閑静なオフィス街にあるビル内の施設です。", class: "photocard__text__textarea"}
    .float-bottom__container
      .float-bottom__line
      .float-bottom__content
        = f.submit "保存して戻る", class: "btn btn-default button-base__button-component gray-btn"
        = f.submit "保存して進む", class: "btn btn-default button-base__button-component green-btn"
